<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Blockstreet — Launchpad Redesign Direction</title>
  <style>
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'TT Firs Neue';
      src: url('TT_Firs_Neue_Regular.woff') format('woff');
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: normal;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'TT Firs Neue';
      src: url('TT_Firs_Neue_Medium.woff') format('woff');
      font-weight: 500;
      font-style: normal;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'TT Firs Neue';
      src: url('TT_Firs_Neue_DemiBold.woff') format('woff');
      font-weight: 600;
      font-style: normal;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --yellow: #FFBA00;
      --yellow-dim: rgba(255,186,0,0.12);
      --yellow-border: rgba(255,186,0,0.25);
      --bg: #111213;
      --bg-elevated: #18191B;
      --bg-card: #1B1D1F;
      --bg-card-2: #202224;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --border-2: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --text: #F0F0F0;
      --muted: #888;
      --muted-2: #555;
      --green: #3ECF8E;
      --red: #E5484D;
      --blue: #3B82F6;
      --purple: #9B8AFB;
      --orange: #F97316;
      --cyan: #22D3EE;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'TT Firs Neue', -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a { color: var(--yellow); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .container { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

    .topbar {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(17,18,19,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .topbar-inner {
      max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 12px 24px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .topbar-left {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 26px; height: 26px;
      background: var(--yellow); border-radius: 6px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: #111; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .topbar-title {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--muted);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    }
    .topbar-title span { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
    .topbar-sep { color: var(--muted-2); }
    .topbar-badge {
      padding: 3px 10px;
      background: var(--yellow-dim);
      border: 1px solid var(--yellow-border);
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--yellow);
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 120px 0 64px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .hero-overline {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--yellow); margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 52px; font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -1.5px;
      color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 20px;
      max-width: 760px;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 620px; line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-verdict {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
      max-width: 620px;
    }
    .verdict-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; min-width: 36px;
      background: rgba(62,207,142,0.12);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .verdict-text {
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .verdict-text strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

    .section {
      padding: 64px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .section:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted-2); margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section h2 {
      font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.6px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .section-desc {
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 620px; margin-bottom: 36px; line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .mismatch-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .mismatch-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .mismatch-card.critical {
      border-color: rgba(229,72,77,0.3);
    }
    .mismatch-num {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--muted-2); letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .mismatch-card h3 {
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px;
      letter-spacing: -0.2px;
    }
    .mismatch-card p {
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .mismatch-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .tag-remove { background: rgba(229,72,77,0.12); color: var(--red); }
    .tag-restructure { background: rgba(255,186,0,0.12); color: var(--yellow); }
    .tag-new { background: rgba(62,207,142,0.12); color: var(--green); }
    .tag-expand { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12); color: var(--blue); }

    .nav-diagram,
    .state-machine,
    .pipeline,
    .solana-panel {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 32px;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .nav-row {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }
    .nav-row-label {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--muted-2); letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase; width: 80px; min-width: 80px;
    }
    .nav-item {
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .nav-keep { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: var(--text); }
    .nav-new { background: rgba(62,207,142,0.1); color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(62,207,142,0.2); }
    .nav-remove { background: rgba(229,72,77,0.08); color: var(--red); text-decoration: line-through; opacity: 0.6; }
    .nav-merge { background: rgba(155,138,251,0.1); color: var(--purple); border: 1px solid rgba(155,138,251,0.2); }
    .flow-arrow { color: var(--muted-2); font-size: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; }
    .nav-legend {
      display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .legend-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted);
    }
    .legend-dot {
      width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .state-flow {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .state-node {
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      position: relative;
      min-width: 120px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .state-node .state-num {
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      opacity: 0.5;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .state-scheduled { background: rgba(255,186,0,0.1); color: var(--yellow); border: 1px solid rgba(255,186,0,0.2); }
    .state-phase1 { background: rgba(155,138,251,0.1); color: var(--purple); border: 1px solid rgba(155,138,251,0.2); }
    .state-phase2 { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); color: var(--blue); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2); }
    .state-sold-invested { background: rgba(62,207,142,0.1); color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(62,207,142,0.2); }
    .state-sold-not { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .state-failed { background: rgba(229,72,77,0.1); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(229,72,77,0.2); }
    .state-claim { background: rgba(34,211,238,0.1); color: var(--cyan); border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,0.2); }
    .state-cta {
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 500;
      opacity: 0.65;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .flow-branch {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px dashed var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .state-detail-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .state-detail,
    .solana-card {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .state-detail-label,
    .solana-card-label {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .state-detail-cta,
    .solana-card p {
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .pipeline-flow {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      align-items: stretch;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .pipeline-step {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: relative;
    }
    .pipeline-step:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .pipeline-step-num {
      width: 28px; height: 28px;
      background: var(--yellow-dim);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--yellow);
      margin: 0 auto 10px;
    }
    .pipeline-step h4 {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .pipeline-step p {
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .access-metrics {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .metric-box {
      padding: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .metric-box .val {
      font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--yellow);
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .metric-box .lbl {
      font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .solana-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .solana-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .chain-tag,
    .status-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .chain-tag.solana { color: var(--cyan); border-color: rgba(34,211,238,0.2); background: rgba(34,211,238,0.08); }
    .status-pill.invested { color: var(--green); border-color: rgba(62,207,142,0.2); background: rgba(62,207,142,0.08); }
    .status-pill.not-invested { color: var(--muted); }

    .screen-list {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;
    }
    .screen-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .screen-card-header {
      padding: 18px 22px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
    }
    .screen-card-header:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
    .screen-card-left {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    }
    .screen-icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .screen-card h3 {
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.2px;
    }
    .screen-card .screen-sub {
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted);
    }
    .priority-badge {
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .p-critical { background: rgba(229,72,77,0.12); color: var(--red); }
    .p-high { background: rgba(249,115,22,0.12); color: var(--orange); }
    .p-medium { background: rgba(255,186,0,0.12); color: var(--yellow); }
    .p-new { background: rgba(62,207,142,0.12); color: var(--green); }
    .screen-card-body {
      padding: 0 22px 22px;
      display: none;
    }
    .screen-card.open .screen-card-body { display: block; }
    .screen-card .chevron {
      color: var(--muted-2);
      transition: transform 0.2s;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .screen-card.open .chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }
    .change-list {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
      padding-top: 8px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .change-item {
      display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start;
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .change-icon {
      width: 20px; height: 20px; min-width: 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 10px; margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .ci-remove { background: rgba(229,72,77,0.12); color: var(--red); }
    .ci-add { background: rgba(62,207,142,0.12); color: var(--green); }
    .ci-change { background: rgba(255,186,0,0.12); color: var(--yellow); }
    .ci-keep { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: var(--muted); }

    .cta-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .cta-table th {
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--muted-2); letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase; padding: 10px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .cta-table td {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    .cta-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .cta-table .state-col { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
    .cta-btn-sample {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .cta-active { background: var(--yellow); color: #111; }
    .cta-disabled { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: var(--muted-2); }
    .cta-danger { background: rgba(229,72,77,0.12); color: var(--red); }
    .cta-info { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12); color: var(--blue); }

    .priority-timeline {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 24px;
    }
    .priority-timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 7px; top: 8px; bottom: 8px;
      width: 2px;
      background: var(--border);
    }
    .priority-item {
      position: relative;
      padding: 16px 0 16px 24px;
    }
    .priority-item::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -20px; top: 22px;
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--yellow);
      border: 2px solid var(--bg);
    }
    .priority-item.done::before { background: var(--green); }
    .priority-item.upcoming::before { background: var(--muted-2); }
    .priority-item h4 {
      font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .priority-item p {
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .priority-phase {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--yellow); letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .question-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--yellow-border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .question-card h4 {
      font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .question-card p {
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .question-num {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--yellow); letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .page-footer {
      padding: 48px 0 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .page-footer p {
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted-2);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .pipeline-flow { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .solana-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 36px; }
      .mismatch-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .pipeline-flow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .pipeline-step { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .access-metrics { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .state-flow { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      .flow-branch { grid-template-columns: 1fr; width: 100%; }
      .state-detail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-inner">
      <div class="topbar-left">
        <div class="logo-icon">B</div>
        <div class="topbar-title">
          <span>Blockstreet</span>
          <span class="topbar-sep">/</span>
          Launchpad Redesign Direction
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="topbar-badge">Internal</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-overline">Product Audit — March 2026</div>
      <h1>Launchpad Redesign<br>Direction</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Structural audit and implementation roadmap for the Blockstreet launchpad. Six core mismatches identified, confirmed pool states mapped, screen-by-screen changes documented, and Solana support planned as a separate system layer.</p>
      <div class="hero-verdict">
        <div class="verdict-icon">✓</div>
        <div class="verdict-text">
          <strong>Visual system is premium and worth keeping.</strong> Dark theme, gold accents, card system, and general layout quality are solid. The problems are structural, not aesthetic.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-label">Diagnosis</div>
      <h2>Six Structural Mismatches</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Cross-referenced every screenshot against confirmed product logic. These need resolution before any visual polish.</p>

      <div class="mismatch-grid">
        <div class="mismatch-card critical">
          <div class="mismatch-num">Issue 01</div>
          <h3>Dual staking references everywhere</h3>
          <p>Homepage hero pillars, How It Works, and stats still reference a system that has already been replaced by single staking and points-based access.</p>
          <span class="mismatch-tag tag-remove">Remove</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mismatch-card critical">
          <div class="mismatch-num">Issue 02</div>
          <h3>Tier system still appears in profile</h3>
          <p>The old tier badge still appears in profile and wallet views. Tiers have been removed in favor of lock duration, multiplier, points, rank, and access status.</p>
          <span class="mismatch-tag tag-remove">Remove</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mismatch-card">
          <div class="mismatch-num">Issue 03</div>
          <h3>Navigation mixes marketing and app logic</h3>
          <p>How It Works, Pools, Portfolio, and founder actions currently sit too close together. The structure needs clearer separation between support pages and operational product views.</p>
          <span class="mismatch-tag tag-restructure">Restructure</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mismatch-card">
          <div class="mismatch-num">Issue 04</div>
          <h3>Pool states are incomplete</h3>
          <p>Current design lacks distinct handling for Sold Out (not invested), Failed / Refund, and post-invest claim states. It also does not differentiate invested sold-out from generic sold-out.</p>
          <span class="mismatch-tag tag-expand">Expand</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mismatch-card">
