          </div>
          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <div class="pipeline-step-num">2</div>
            <h4>Lock Duration</h4>
            <p>Longer lock periods increase the multiplier applied to the stake.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pipeline-step">
            <div class="pipeline-step-num">3</div>
