            <p>Main wallet remains the staking reference wallet. If a pool is Solana-based, the user adds a Solana wallet as an optional participation wallet. The UI should make it explicit that the main wallet is for identity and staking reference, while the Solana wallet is required for participation on that chain.</p>
            <div class="solana-tags">
              <span class="chain-tag solana">Solana Pool</span>
